Wow! Great recipe! The people who are complaining about it being too salty did not read the recipe. It clearly states "Add 2 to 3 tablespoons salt and the spaghetti". To the water...not the sauce! So if you're saying you followed the recipe EXACTLY, you didn't. It's not fair to say it's a bad recipe if you prepared it incorrectly. I've screwed up myself lots of times by not reading it clearly enough. Try it again. I'd bet you like it. And so easy!

